      <title>欧洲股票对关税延迟乐观，欧洲央行削减降低</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/european-stocks-advance-as-auto-shares-rally-on-tariffs-delay</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲股票早些时候会因潜在的关税延迟而下降，而欧洲中央银行则按预期降低了利率，并表明其还原阶段正在结束。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/european-stocks-advance-as-auto-shares-rally-on-tariffs-delay</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Mar 2025 08:17:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢特尼克（Lutnick）发出信号特朗普可能会退缩关税时，石油会波动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-march-6</link>
      <description><![CDATA[正如美国商务部长霍华德·卢特尼克（Howard Lutnick）一样，石油在收益和损失之间倾斜，继续进行一系列动荡的会议，特朗普政府可能会减轻对该国两个最大贸易伙伴的关税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-march-6</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Mar 2025 23:29:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股票修剪损失随着关税谈话沉没的美元：市场包装</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华尔街继续面临关税头条新闻的巨大波动，在美国两个最大的贸易伙伴可能会缓刑的情况下，股票减少了损失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Mar 2025 22:36:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
